Package edu.mills.openstudio

Implementation of the app OpenStudio and the classes necessary to allow you to search and add art studios on a map.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApiInterface
    Interface for GET and POST API calls.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutActivity
    About page introducing OpenStudio.
    AddStudioActivity
    Form for users to add new studios.
    ApiClient
    Client to process Retrofit requests.
    DetailStudioActivity
    Shows the details of selected studio.
    FindStudioActivity
    Provide a place for users to view and search for studios based on their locations.
    HttpRequestHandler
    Handles sending HTTP requests and getting responses.
    ImageDetailActivity
    Class to hold studio images.
    LoginActivity
    User login page.
    MainActivity
    Home page where users can choose to navigate to studios, workshops and tools.
    RegisterActivity
    User registration page.
    SessionManager
    Monitor if the user is logged into their account.
    SplashActivity
    Activity to launch OpenStudio splash screen.
    SQLiteHandler
    Handles the creation and opening of user authentication information.
    Studio
    Defines the format of a studio for Retrofit JSON parsing.
    StudioListActivity
    Show studios in listview.
    StudioResponse
    Defines the format of a response from a studio API call for Retrofit JSON parsing.
    User
    Defines the format of a user for Retrofit JSON parsing.
    UserHomeScreenActivity
    User home screen.
    UserResponse
    Defines the format of a response from a studio API call for Retrofit JSON parsing.

Package edu.mills.openstudio Description

Implementation of the app OpenStudio and the classes necessary to allow you to search and add art studios on a map. Created for Mills CS 115: Mobile Application Development, Spring 2017 by Nadine Bui, Synali Parker, Regina Wang, and Eve Gottwald
